---
import GlobalMixcloudPlayer from "../components/GlobalMixcloudPlayer.astro";
---

<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta  
      name="description"
      content="Bio of Itchy Lemon — Portuguese DJ and electronic music producer shaped by melodic tension, deep groove and underground club energy."
    />
    <meta name="author" content="Itchy Lemon" />
    <meta name="theme-color" content="#07090c" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Bio | Itchy Lemon</title>
    <link rel="icon" type="image/png" href="/favicon.png" />
    <link rel="canonical" href="https://itchy-lemon.pages.dev/bio" />

    <style>
      :root {
        --bg: #07090c;
        --bg-soft: #10141b;
        --text: #f4f4f0;
        --muted: #a7adb8;
        --acid: #d8ff3e;
        --line: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.12);
      }

      * {
        box-sizing: border-box;
      }

      body {
        margin: 0;
        font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;
        background:
          radial-gradient(circle at top right, rgba(216, 255, 62, 0.12), transparent 34%),
          linear-gradient(135deg, #07090c 0%, #111827 48%, #050608 100%);
        color: var(--text);
        min-height: 100vh;
      }

      a {
        color: inherit;
        text-decoration: none;
      }

      .page {
        min-height: 100vh;
        padding: 32px;
      }

      header {
        display: flex;
        justify-content: space-between;
        align-items: center;
        gap: 24px;
        padding-bottom: 56px;
      }

      .logo {
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        gap: 10px;
        color: var(--acid);
        font-weight: 700;
        text-transform: uppercase;
        white-space: nowrap;
      }

      .logo-icon {
        display: block;
        width: 22px;
        height: 22px;
        object-fit: contain;
        flex-shrink: 0;
      }

      .logo span {
        display: inline-block;
        font-size: 14px;
        letter-spacing: 0.32em;
        line-height: 1;
      }

      nav {
        display: flex;
        gap: 22px;
        font-size: 13px;
        text-transform: uppercase;
        letter-spacing: 0.12em;
        color: var(--muted);
      }

      nav a:hover,
      nav a.active {
        color: var(--acid);
      }

      main {
        max-width: 1080px;
        margin: 0 auto;
      }

      .eyebrow {
        color: var(--acid);
        text-transform: uppercase;
        letter-spacing: 0.24em;
        font-size: 13px;
        margin-bottom: 18px;
      }

      h1 {
        margin: 0;
        font-size: clamp(48px, 8vw, 104px);
        line-height: 0.9;
        letter-spacing: -0.06em;
        text-transform: uppercase;
      }

      .lead {
        margin-top: 32px;
        max-width: 860px;
        font-size: clamp(22px, 3vw, 34px);
        line-height: 1.16;
        color: var(--text);
      }

      .content-grid {
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: 0.75fr 1.25fr;
        gap: 48px;
        margin-top: 72px;
      }

      .panel {
        border: 1px solid var(--line);
        background: rgba(16, 20, 27, 0.72);
        border-radius: 28px;
        padding: 28px;
        height: fit-content;
        backdrop-filter: blur(12px);
      }

      .panel h2,
      .text-block h2 {
        margin: 0 0 18px;
        font-size: 13px;
        letter-spacing: 0.18em;
        text-transform: uppercase;
        color: var(--acid);
      }

      .highlight-list {
        display: grid;
        gap: 18px;
        margin: 0;
        padding: 0;
        list-style: none;
      }

      .highlight-list li {
        border-top: 1px solid var(--line);
        padding-top: 16px;
        color: var(--muted);
        line-height: 1.55;
      }

      .highlight-list strong {
        display: block;
        color: var(--text);
        margin-bottom: 4px;
      }

      .text-block {
        color: var(--muted);
        font-size: 17px;
        line-height: 1.75;
      }

      .text-block p {
        margin: 0 0 22px;
      }

      .text-block strong {
        color: var(--text);
      }

      .quote {
        margin-top: 38px;
        border-left: 2px solid var(--acid);
        padding-left: 22px;
        color: var(--text);
        font-size: 24px;
        line-height: 1.25;
        letter-spacing: -0.02em;
      }

      .bio-links {
        display: flex;
        flex-wrap: wrap;
        gap: 12px;
        margin-top: 34px;
      }

      .bio-link {
        border: 1px solid var(--line);
        border-radius: 999px;
        padding: 11px 15px;
        color: var(--muted);
        font-size: 13px;
      }

      .bio-link:hover {
        color: #050608;
        background: var(--acid);
        border-color: var(--acid);
      }

      footer {
        max-width: 1080px;
        margin: 80px auto 0;
        color: var(--muted);
        font-size: 12px;
        padding-top: 28px;
        border-top: 1px solid var(--line);
        display: flex;
        justify-content: space-between;
        gap: 20px;
      }

      @media (max-width: 860px) {
        .page {
          padding: 22px;
        }

        header {
          align-items: flex-start;
          flex-direction: column;
        }

        nav {
          flex-wrap: wrap;
        }

        .content-grid {
          grid-template-columns: 1fr;
          gap: 32px;
          margin-top: 48px;
        }

        footer {
          flex-direction: column;
        }
      }
    </style>
  </head>

  <body>
    <div class="page">
      <header>
        <a class="logo" href="/" aria-label="Itchy Lemon homepage">
          <img class="logo-icon" src="/favicon.png" alt="" />
          <span>Itchy Lemon</span>
        </a>

        <nav>
          <a href="/music">Music</a>
          <a class="active" href="/bio">Bio</a>
          <a href="/discography">Discography</a>
          <a href="/media">Media</a>
          <a href="/press-kit">Press Kit</a>
          <a href="/sets">Sets</a>
          <a href="/booking">Booking</a>
        </nav>
      </header>

      <main>
        <p class="eyebrow">Artist Biography</p>

        <h1>Bio</h1>

        <p class="lead">
          Itchy Lemon is a Portuguese DJ and electronic music producer with a sound shaped by melodic tension, deep groove and underground club energy.
        </p>

        <section class="content-grid">
          <aside class="panel">
            <h2>Highlights</h2>

            <ul class="highlight-list">
              <li>
                <strong>Artist name</strong>
                Itchy Lemon
              </li>

              <li>
                <strong>Based in Portugal</strong>
                DJ sets, original productions, guest mixes and selected collaborations.
              </li>

              <li>
                <strong>Sound identity</strong>
                Melodic house, deep electronic grooves, progressive movement and underground energy.
              </li>

              <li>
                <strong>Music platforms</strong>
                Present across Spotify, Beatport, Traxsource, SoundCloud, YouTube and social channels.
              </li>

              <li>
                <strong>Current focus</strong>
                Repositioning the project with a renewed digital presence, EPK and booking-ready structure.
              </li>
            </ul>
          </aside>

          <section class="text-block">
            <h2>Short Bio</h2>

            <p>
              <strong>Itchy Lemon</strong> is the artistic project of a Portuguese DJ and producer with a long-standing connection to electronic music, club culture and independent music production.
            </p>

            <p>
              Rooted in melodic house, deep grooves and progressive electronic textures, his sound moves between introspection and dancefloor energy — music built with atmosphere, rhythm and emotional progression at its core.
            </p>

            <p>
              Over the years, the project has developed through DJ sets, original productions, remixes and releases across digital music platforms, with artist presence on Beatport, Traxsource, Spotify, SoundCloud and YouTube.
            </p>

            <p>
              In 2026, Itchy Lemon is being repositioned with a renewed visual identity and a sharper digital presence, bringing the project closer to promoters, curators, radio shows, labels and selected collaborators.
            </p>

            <p>
              The current direction is clear: melodic, deep and underground electronic music with intent — designed for club movement, emotional build-up and carefully selected sonic journeys.
            </p>

            <div class="quote">
              Melodic, deep and underground — electronic music with emotion, groove and intent.
            </div>

            <div class="bio-links" aria-label="Artist links">
              <a class="bio-link" href="/music">Music</a>
              <a class="bio-link" href="/discography">Discography</a>
              <a class="bio-link" href="/press-kit">Press Kit</a>
              <a class="bio-link" href="/booking">Booking</a>
              <a class="bio-link" href="https://open.spotify.com/artist/5IfFyzIiz1iBO7RZUJyFen" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer">Spotify</a>
              <a class="bio-link" href="https://www.instagram.com/itchy_lemon/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer">Instagram</a>
            </div>
          </section>
        </section>
      </main>

      <footer>
        <span>© 2026 Itchy Lemon. All rights reserved.</span>
        <span>
          Official Website & EPK · Portugal ·
          <a href="/privacy-policy">Privacy Policy</a>
        </span>
      </footer>
    </div>

    <GlobalMixcloudPlayer />
  </body>
</html>